{"type": "article", "id": 24446, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 25379, "name": "Stefan Diez Office"}, {"id": 25380, "name": "Kvadrat"}, {"id": 25381, "name": "Debra Folz Design"}, {"id": 25382, "name": "Ink + Mortar"}, {"id": 25383, "name": "Studio Oddness"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 24952, "name": "Tsoi Man Hei Ken"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134955v7GcEzCDkI8yJS52.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Soba by Stefan Diez Office</h2>\n<p>这是日本创意机构 Stefan Diez Office 发起的竹家具系列项目，他们保留了竹子本来的样子。特别之处在于在桌椅等支柱结构上做了掏空处理，弯曲之后恰好可插入一根横向的竹子，以此来构成一种结构。竹家具是通过芳纶绳固定的，在三角形桌腿之间充当梁的结构。桌面用上了玻璃，而没有任何金属，尽量保持自然的竹筒效果。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153744gvZruWTpjcqaXiBY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153745CoZAE8IT6fL9abVl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40042373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153745SO6ypTQMF9vlJ4bf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153745WyRj8m5XA9xSTdLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40042373\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153746gAhKm4TB5YxHz8fE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Reflex &amp; Pulsar &amp; Fuse by Raf Simons &amp; Kvadrat </h2>\n<p>这是比利时的时装设计师 Raf Simons  和丹麦纺织品牌 Kvadrat 推出的新品条纹面料。选用非常现代的鲜艳的颜色，多数是用一种颜色进行深浅对比，比如大红和橙红，深蓝和晶蓝，也有一些灰色调和中性色调，在活泼中不失协调。用这种面料来装饰意大利建筑师 Franco Albini 的吊椅时会非常活泼。<a href=\"http://kvadrat.dk/products/new\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153746IfeHqj4akDVxA3wK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66755319\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153747xjDvgfKzpr0YutwX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66548673\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153747WzxDEv4qjawhLHAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153748s7ncm4TpeJbRGzrC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153748MNVBJfYcrjGvoZS9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Drape by Debra Folz Design</h2>\n<p>这组桌子像是一张桌布，它是方形的，平整光滑，四个角都有小的折叠感。桌面下是纤细的金属结构，与桌面在材料和颜色上都产生对比，突出了桌面的轻盈，像是变魔术的道具。他们另有一款八边形的玻璃桌，支撑结构类似但更有棱角，玻璃桌面的边缘处有一些重叠的颜色，是想模拟钻石与光线之间的感觉。<a href=\"http://www.debrafolz.com\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153749TvMWiHxX2dLNjqFh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153750nGUrgbVRwfMv6ItZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153750jgkxVZClipNJ3rY7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153750njLmQuXDETOywA78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153751iBc42rCxz7oUAhbS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.16\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Heli-Trivet by Tsoi Man Hei Ken</h2>\n<p>这是一个隔热的小工具，绿色部分是硅材料。将它平摊后呈现出十字型，可以承担温度很高的铁锅以及多种型号。沿着中间的圆环拉起来后，四个扇叶则会因金属的重力而朝下，像一个三脚架，有方便悬挂的特征，简单而实用。<a href=\"http://www.hktdc.com/suppliers-products/Heli-Trivet-Heat-Resistant-Mat/en/1X002R5M/2829998/\">点击这里尝试购买。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153751eZlqKg6nU7INyRuY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071537526yPMR1q3Y0iC8OVK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153752pdvlNVSKsgGq2XMJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.36857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Bubblegraphy by Studio Oddness</h2>\n<p>这组陶瓷花瓶来自荷兰两个年轻人，花瓶的形状很普通却有气泡一样的蓝色花纹。他们创造了一种特殊的上釉方式得以将肥皂泡的自然状态印在花瓶上，可以看到颜色深浅和形状大小都不均匀的图案，都有些偶然和随机，看起来很自然。它打破传统花瓶图案的精致和程式化，也很特别。<a href=\"http://www.oddness.nl/index.html\">这里是工作室链接</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153753TxHJjvZbsYd1VDcl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153753xhX5ovwdApYPVLqc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153754AMov6sfHdO75ImxR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153754aLurZyqdTHD13hnJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153755RcP9QdoO4ZvJA1WC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>CORA by Ink + Mortar</h2>\n<p>这是为女生生理周期使用的棉塞而设计的包装，但它完全没有任何常见的少女粉红色调。棉塞的小袋子包装极具几何图形的线条感，很小巧，它另配有专门放棉塞的方形盒子，是纯黑色的，在简洁大方中凸显出优雅自然。这个项目的初衷是想为不发达地区的女性也带来方便，让她们在心理上不会觉得异样。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153755p1c0giIotzZhj8Kl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153756fqUhIw0XA9olO54R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060715375607rWeIs1RiGShOxT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153757Rf8sp6NDTtv9Z0al.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153757q5dyex7loi3QZcCv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153757SNvVOMCi0cF9jWgf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n\n\n"}